default2.7 
defaultOur review
default of the links between poverty, ethnicity and education examined not only levels of attainment at d
defaultifferent ages, but also how children’s progress through school varied. In addition to ethnicity and free school meal status, the review examined the role played by gender. 
default(**See note below regarding the way in which we approach the issues of ethnicity and
default ethnic categorisation). 
