default2.18 
defaultFor those who 
defaultcontinue in education, the type of institution they attend has an influence on their later higher education choices and outcomes. Fewer students from FE colleges are accepted by universities than from School Sixth Forms and there is some evidence that stud
defaultents from FE colleges tend to achieve lower classes of degree
